        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:14.900",
        "end": "00:18.000",
        "original": "本日の生誕祭ライブの後も...",
        "english": "Even after today's birthday live...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:18.000",
        "end": "00:21.500",
        "original": "...お楽しみはまだまだ続きます。",
        "english": "...the fun will continue.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:22.000",
        "end": "00:25.800",
        "original": "なんと、ホロアースにて特別企画...",
        "english": "Surprisingly, a special project in Holoearth...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:25.800",
        "end": "00:30.500",
        "original": "...「アキー・ローゼンタール生誕祭アンコール in ホロアース」...",
        "english": "...\"Aki Rosenthal Birthday Live Encore in Holoearth\"...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:30.500",
        "end": "00:33.500",
        "original": "...を開催しまーす！",
        "english": "...will be held!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:34.000",
        "end": "00:39.500",
        "original": "今回初披露した新曲『モノポリー』をホロアースで歌っちゃいます！",
        "english": "I'll sing the new song \"Monopoly\" that I performed for the first time today in Holoearth!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:40.000",
        "end": "00:43.500",
        "original": "色んな角度からアキロゼのパフォーマンスや演出を...",
        "english": "Akirose's performance and production from various angles...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:43.500",
        "end": "00:46.500",
        "original": "...じっくりと見てみてくださいね。",
        "english": "...please take a close look at them.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:47.300",
        "end": "00:50.500",
        "original": "さらに、ホロアースだけのMCパートもたっぷりあるので...",
        "english": "Furthermore, there's plenty of MC parts only in Holoearth...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:50.500",
        "end": "00:53.600",
        "original": "...ぜひぜひ会いに来てください！",
        "english": "...so please come and see me!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:54.400",
        "end": "00:58.200",
        "original": "開催日は3月13日、3月13日です！",
        "english": "The date is March 13th, March 13th!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:59.000",
