        "original": "詳細はホロアース公式Xをチェックしてね！",
        "english": "Check the Holoearth official X for details!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:03.500",
        "end": "01:05.800",
        "original": "そして、最後のお知らせが！",
        "english": "And, the final announcement!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:06.100",
        "end": "01:08.300",
        "original": "新曲『モノポリー』！",
        "english": "New song, \"Monopoly\"!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:08.400",
        "end": "01:12.300",
        "original": "本日日付が変わる頃にリリースされますので...",
        "english": "It will be released around the time the date changes today...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:12.300",
        "end": "01:18.100",
        "original": "...各音楽配信サービスからぜひ購入してね！たくさん聴いてね！",
        "english": "...so please purchase it from various music distribution services! Listen to it a lot!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:18.900",
        "end": "01:22.100",
        "original": "振付も歌もとってもキャッチーなので...",
        "english": "The choreography and the song are both very catchy...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:22.100",
        "end": "01:26.900",
        "original": "...覚えてみんなで楽しんでもらえる、愛されるような楽曲になってくれたら...",
        "english": "...I hope it becomes a beloved song that everyone can remember and enjoy together...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:26.900",
        "end": "01:29.300",
        "original": "...嬉しいなーって思っています。",
        "english": "...I'd be happy if it did.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:30.100",
        "end": "01:32.400",
        "original": "また、後日ライブ配信で...",
        "english": "Also, in a later live stream...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:32.400",
        "end": "01:35.400",
        "original": "...新曲『モノポリー』だったり、今回のライブに触れた後日談など...",
        "english": "...I'd like to talk about the new song \"Monopoly\" and behind-the-scenes stories from this live...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:35.400",
        "end": "01:40.000",
        "original": "...語ったり、一緒に見たりなどしたいなと思っているのーで...",
        "english": "...and watch it together with you...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:40.100",
        "end": "01:44.200",
        "original": "...ぜひチャンネル登録、高評価ポチ、通知もオン！",
        "english": "...so please subscribe to the channel, hit the like button, and turn on notifications!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:44.200",
        "end": "01:46.600",
        "original": "し、忘れてた人は、今ポチッとしてね！",
        "english": "If you forgot, hit it now!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:47.100",
        "end": "01:49.600",
        "original": "絶対絶対また会いに来てね！",
        "english": "Make sure to come and see me again!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:50.300",
        "end": "01:51.500",
        "original": "それでは。",
        "english": "Well then.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:51.900",
