        "original": "運命は時に残酷。",
        "english": "Fate is sometimes cruel.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:54.800",
        "end": "01:58.500",
        "original": "あなたが選びたくて選んだものではないかもしれない。",
        "english": "It may not be something you wanted to choose.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:58.900",
        "end": "02:03.200",
        "original": "だけど、いつでもあなたの人生はあなたのもの。",
        "english": "But your life is always yours.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
